TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select etl_id, BRIEF_DESCRIPTION, category, close_time, COMMODITY, contact_name, date_ack, date_rec, DEPT, FIRST_CALL, incident_id, location, open, open_time, Opened_by, owner_name, pfz_call_source, pfz_division, pfz_full_name, pfz_notify_method, pfz_orig_group, pfz_rb_full_name, pfz_related_projects, pfz_sla_title, pfz_vip, PROBLEM_TYPE, PRODUCT_type, RESOLUTION_CODE, SUBCATEGORY, update_time, case WHEN pfz_division is null then 'OTHER' WHEN pfz_division in ('LEGAL', 'CORP LEGAL') then 'LEGAL' WHEN pfz_division in ('AHG', 'PAH', 'ANHLTH-PHL') then 'PAH' WHEN pfz_division in ('CHC', 'PCH', 'CONSHC-PHL', 'CONSUMER HEALTH') then 'PCH' WHEN pfz_division in ('CER', 'CHR (CER)', 'CORP HR', 'CORPORATE HUMAN RESOURCES') then 'CHR' WHEN pfz_division = 'CORP AFFAIRS' then 'CORP AFFAIRS' WHEN pfz_division in ('CIT', 'CONTROLLERS', 'FINANCE', 'TREASURERS') then 'CORP FINANCE' WHEN pfz_division like 'CORP%' then 'CORP FINANCE' WHEN pfz_division = 'PGM' then 'PGM' WHEN pfz_division in ('PARK-DAVIS', 'PGRD') then 'PGRD' WHEN pfz_division in ('FIELD SALES', 'PPG', 'PGP') then 'PGP' ELSE 'OTHER' END standard_division from stg_incidentsm1, call_time where etl_id = (select max(etl_id) from call_time)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT ASSIGNMENTM1.NAME, ASSIGNMENTM1.PFZ_SITE_ID, PFZSITESM1.PFZ_REGION_ID, ASSIGNMENTM1.PFZ_REPORTING_GROUP FROM ASSIGNMENTM1, PFZSITESM1 where assignmentm1.pfz_site_id = pfzsitesm1.site_id

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT STG_LOCATIONM1.STG_LOCATION, STG_LOCATIONM1.STG_COUNTRY, STG_LOCATIONM1.TIME_ZONE, STG_LOCATIONM1.STG_LOCATION_CODE, STG_LOCATIONM1.STG_LOCATION_NAME FROM STG_LOCATIONM1 where stg_location not in (select location from mut_gps)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
